ve companion. We find a smaller inclination\nangle of the inner disk of TW Hya than that determined for the outer disk,\nsuggestive of a disk warp. We also detect significant azimuthal asymmetries in\nthe SR 21 and HD 135344B inner disks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 May 2008 17:18:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
