 The apparent 18O/17O gradient along the galactic disc and the\ndiscrepancy between outer disc and LMC isotope ratios may be explained by\ndifferent ages of the respective stellar populations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 May 2008 07:47:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
